ragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"[Danvers, Massachusetts, Sep 19th, 2019] MAXAM is proud to announce the release of the updated MAXAM Global Website in conjunction with the launch of the all-new ","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"[Danvers, Massachusetts, Sep 19th, 2019] MAXAM is proud to announce the release of the updated MAXAM Global Website in conjunction with the launch of the all-new ","href":null},{"type":"text","text":{"content":"MAXAM Global Customer Portal","link":{"url":"https://b2b.maxamtire.com/"}},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"MAXAM Global Customer Portal","href":"https://b2b.maxamtire.com/"},{"type":"text","text":{"content":". In continual efforts to improve the customer experience and stay true to the MAXAM mission of being a Business Solutions Provider, the new portal has been designed to provide the industry with revolutionary customer service. ","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":". In continual efforts to improve the customer experience and stay true to the MAXAM mission of being a Business Solutions Provider, the new portal has been designed to provide the industry with revolutionary customer service. ","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81e5-84cf-dec3e23dab91","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-818e-be43-cea350678c88"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:00:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:00:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":" The MAXAM Global Customer Portal was designed to be a cutting edge 24/7 self-service, online site featuring easy-to-use navigation, effective user options, support and capability. “We've changed the way of thinking and are advancing how the specialty tire industry can transact and simplify their daily business routines. Our goal remains to be the best Business Solutions Provider in the industry and our customers can expect continued advancement from our team, products and technology,\" says Troy Kline, President of MAXAM Tire North America, Inc.  ","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":" The MAXAM Global Customer Portal was designed to be a cutting edge 24/7 self-service, online site featuring easy-to-use navigation, effective user options, support and capability. “We've changed the way of thinking and are advancing how the specialty tire industry can transact and simplify their daily business routines. Our goal remains to be the best Business Solutions Provider in the industry and our customers can expect continued advancement from our team, products and technology,\" says Troy Kline, President of MAXAM Tire North America, Inc.  ","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-81a3-ad65-dd51db3b3b4e","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-818e-be43-cea350678c88"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:00:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:00:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"MAXAM released a beta version of the customer portal earlier this year and continued to make minor enhancements based on customer feedback. Since April 2019, the portal has been open to the public and as of September 2019, 10% of MAXAM’s invoices are transacting through the new portal. ","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"MAXAM released a beta version of the customer portal earlier this year and continued to make minor enhancements based on customer feedback. Since April 2019, the portal has been open to the public and as of September 2019, 10% of MAXAM’s invoices are transacting through the new portal. ","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived":false},{"object":"block","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8112-8cde-dc4fa0eb2c35","parent":{"type":"page_id","page_id":"35534d6d-7cea-818e-be43-cea350678c88"},"created_time":"2026-05-03T22:00:00.000Z","last_edited_time":"2026-05-03T22:00:00.000Z","created_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"last_edited_by":{"object":"user","id":"35534d6d-7cea-8179-8809-002768bc44c3"},"has_children":false,"in_trash":false,"type":"paragraph","paragraph":{"rich_text":[{"type":"text","text":{"content":"The MAXAM Global Customer Portal allows users to easily place their orders with numerous E-Commerce ordering options for LTL and Truckload warehouse orders as well as Factory Direct ordering capabilities. The system also allows customers the option to place back orders from MAXAM’s warehouses along with these additional features: ","link":null},"annotations":{"bold":false,"italic":false,"strikethrough":false,"underline":false,"code":false,"color":"default"},"plain_text":"The MAXAM Global Customer Portal allows users to easily place their orders with numerous E-Commerce ordering options for LTL and Truckload warehouse orders as well as Factory Direct ordering capabilities. The system also allows customers the option to place back orders from MAXAM’s warehouses along with these additional features: ","href":null}],"icon":null,"color":"default"},"archived